INSERT INTO `blog_infos` VALUES (1, 1, '<p><strong>全局安装gulp插件：</strong></p><p>因为gulp是基于<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://nodejs.cn/\" href=\"http://nodejs.cn/\">node.js</a>的，安装好了nodejs前提下，命令提示符执行<strong>npm install gulp -g;</strong></p><p>然后执行<strong>gulp-v</strong>,如果没有出现版本号，<strong>请按照如下步骤来解决：</strong></p><p><br></p><p>总结原因：因为<strong>没有配置gulp的环境变量</strong></p><p><strong>一：查找变量步骤</strong>：</p><p>1：dos输入：<strong>npm config get prefix</strong></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img height=\"116\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/space/2017/0622/104349_ahuy_2645796.png\" src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/space/2017/0622/104349_ahuy_2645796.png\" width=\"917\"></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong>显示的地址就是系统变量path</p><p>2：dos输入：<strong>npm config list</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img height=\"224\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/space/2017/0622/104428_qOEs_2645796.png\" src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/space/2017/0622/104428_qOEs_2645796.png\" width=\"842\"></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在显示的数据中找到prefix属性，等号后面的值就是系统变量PATH（一会添加的时候把里面的\\\\改成\\）</p><p>3：<strong>查找node_global文件路径</strong></p><p>就是自己手动找node_global全局文件路径，根据自己安装nodejs时候文件的位置，找到node_global的位置，这个路径就是系统变量PATH</p><p><strong>二：添加全局变量：</strong></p><p><strong>1：打开环境变量设置（</strong>计算机(右击)-&gt;属性-&gt;高级系统设置 -&gt; 高级-&gt;环境变量<strong>）：</strong></p><p><img height=\"645\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/space/2017/0622/104738_T74v_2645796.png\" src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/space/2017/0622/104738_T74v_2645796.png\" width=\"610\"></p><p>2：<strong>设置gulp变量</strong>：</p><p>在<strong>系统变量PATH</strong>中添加刚才查找的地址</p><p><img height=\"642\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/space/2017/0622/105011_35NX_2645796.png\" src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/space/2017/0622/105011_35NX_2645796.png\" width=\"608\"></p><p>保存之后，重新打开dos窗口输入 gulp -v</p><p><img height=\"88\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/space/2017/0622/105852_FM5B_2645796.png\" src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/space/2017/0622/105852_FM5B_2645796.png\" width=\"961\"></p><p><br></p><p><br data-cke-eol=\"1\"></p>', 0, 0, NULL, 1, 1, '2018-03-02 13:47:18', '2018-11-30 18:15:30');
INSERT INTO `blog_infos` VALUES (2, 2, '<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 解决思路：Maven + gulp +&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"https://github.com/eirslett/frontend-maven-plugin\" href=\"https://github.com/eirslett/frontend-maven-plugin\" target=\"_blank\">frontend-maven-plugin</a></strong></p><ul><li>在项目根目录下添加：gulpfile.js、package.json</li></ul><p>&nbsp;gulpfile.js</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p></p><div tabindex=\"-1\" data-cke-widget-wrapper=\"1\" data-cke-filter=\"off\" class=\"cke_widget_wrapper cke_widget_block cke_widget_selected\" data-cke-display-name=\"代码段\" data-cke-widget-id=\"2\"><pre data-cke-widget-data=\"%7B%22lang%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22var%20gulp%20%3D%20require(\'gulp\')%2C%20%20%2F%2F%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%5Cn%20%20%20%20runSequence%20%3D%20require(\'run-sequence\')%2C%20%2F%2F%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%5Cn%20%20%20%20cssver%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-make-css-url-version\')%2C%20%2F%2F%5Cn%20%20%20%20cssmin%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-minify-css\')%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20jshint%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-jshint\')%2C%2F%2Fjs%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%5Cn%20%20%20%20uglify%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-uglify\')%2C%20%2F%2Fjs%E5%8E%8B%E7%BC%A9%5Cn%20%20%20%20concat%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-concat\')%2C%2F%2Fnpm%20install%20gulp-jshint%20gulp-sass%20gulp-concat%20gulp-uglify%20gulp-rename%20--save-dev%20%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%90%88%E5%B9%B6%5Cn%20%20%20%20clean%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-clean\')%2C%2F%2F%E6%B8%85%E7%A9%BA%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B9%5Cn%20%20%20%20rename%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-rename\')%2C%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%90%8D%5Cn%20%20%20%20rev%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-rev\')%2C%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E5%90%8D%5Cn%20%20%20%20filter%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-filter\')%2C%2F%2F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%5Cn%20%20%20%20zip%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-zip\')%2C%20%2F%2Fzip%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%5Cn%20%20%20%20revCollector%20%3D%20require(\'gulp-rev-collector\')%3B%2F%2Fgulp-rev%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%20%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8Ehtml%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%